==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dissatisfactory
<hw>Dis*sat`is*fac"to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Causing
dissatisfaction; unable to give content; unsatisfactory;
displeasing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To have reduced the different qualifications in the different
States to one uniform rule, would probably have been as
<qex>dissatisfactory</qex> to some of the States, as difficult for the
Convention.</q> <rj><qau>A. Hamilton.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Dis*sat`is*fac"to*ri*ness</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>dissatisfied</ent>⟦br⟧
